OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FAn independent review has found
OL,7,F'repeated failures in the quality of
OL,8,Fcare' within Swansea Bay University
OL,9,FHealth Board's Maternity and Neonatal
OL,10,FServices
OL,12,FThe final report, published today,
OL,13,Falso reveals that whilst many report a
OL,14,Fpositive experience of pregnancy and
OL,15,Fbirth, "some women have, and continue
OL,16,Fto have a considerably poor or
OL,17,Ftraumatic experience".
