OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FThe Health Board's Maternity and
OL,7,FNeonatal services have been the
OL,8,Fsubject of scrutiny since at least
OL,9,F2019 and in the last five years there
OL,10,Fhave been a number of internal and
OL,11,Fexternal reviews.
OL,13,FThe independent review was
OL,14,Fcommissioned in 2023 after the Health
OL,15,FInspectorate for Wales highlighted a
OL,16,Frange of significant concerns about
OL,17,Fmaternity and childbirth within the
OL,18,Fhealth board.
