OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FITV Wales has reported extensively on
OL,7,Fthe experiences of families who have
OL,8,Fused the maternity unit at Swansea's
OL,9,FSingleton Hospital, including the
OL,10,FChannons. Their son Gethin was born
OL,11,Fwith severe brain damage after
OL,12,Fcomplications during his birth in 2019.
OL,14,F'An outlier'
OL,16,FThe report cites data into child
OL,17,Fdeaths, calling the health board an
OL,18,F'outlier' in stillbirth rate and
OL,19,Fneonatal mortality rates for three
OL,20,Fconsecutive years between 2019 and
OL,21,F2021 and then again in 2023.
