OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FBetween 2018 and 2023, SBUHB reported
OL,7,F90 stillbirths and 45 neonatal deaths
OL,8,F(babies who died within 28 days of
OL,9,Fbirth) out of nearly 17,000 deliveries.
OL,11,FStaffing and governance were
OL,12,Fhighlighted in the report.
OL,14,FLow and inconsistent staffing levels
OL,15,Fwere found between 2021 and 2024, with
OL,16,Fa loss of experienced staff after the
OL,17,FCovid-19 pandemic.
