OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FWhilst 'significant weaknesses' in
OL,7,Fgovernance led to a "lack of challenge
OL,8,Fand scrutiny" and "poor visibility of
OL,9,Fissues", including a lack of
OL,10,Fcompassion after women gave birth.
OL,12,FThe complaints handling at SBUHB has
OL,13,Fbeen branded as historically poor and
OL,14,Fincidents investigation 'light touch'.
OL,16,FThe review also highlighted a need for
OL,17,Fimprovements in medical equipment, the
OL,18,Flevel of mixed skill staff and the
OL,19,Fdelays with pain medication.
