OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FIt also discussed how more work is
OL,7,Fneeded to ensure consistent person-
OL,8,Fcentred care is provided, particularly
OL,9,Fin relation to delayed induction.
OL,11,FIt found a lack of neonatal radiology
OL,12,Fexpertise and mental health care, as
OL,13,Fwell as breastfeeding support.
OL,15,FThe review's authors also found too
OL,16,Fmuch reliance of midwives to care for
OL,17,Fpremature babies and a failure in
OL,18,Fcommunication to support those for
OL,19,Fwhom English is not their preferred
OL,20,Flanguage.
