OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FShe said: "We have highlighted
OL,7,Frepeated failures in the quality of
OL,8,Fcare and governance at the Health
OL,9,FBoard and, whilst there are several
OL,10,Fchanges that the Health Board has put
OL,11,Fin place during the last year, there
OL,12,Fremain further actions to be urgently
OL,13,Fprogressed."
OL,15,F"There is still much to be done to
OL,16,Fimprove maternity and neonatal
OL,17,Fservices, and this report serves as a
OL,18,Fcall to action for the Health Board to
OL,19,Fdo more to rapidly improve the
OL,20,Fexperiences of those who use these
OL,21,Fservices."
