OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FChair of Swansea Bay University Health
OL,7,FBoard, Jan Williams has said, "The
OL,8,Ffinal report of the Independent Review
OL,9,Finto our maternity and neonatal
OL,10,Fservices has identified a range of
OL,11,Ffailings and experiences that are
OL,12,Funacceptable and distressing and we
OL,13,Fapologise unreservedly to the women
OL,14,Fand their families who have suffered
OL,15,Fas a result.
OL,17,F"We acknowledge the traumatic and life
OL,18,Fchanging experiences some will have
OL,19,Fexperienced as a result of harm or
OL,20,Floss and offer our heartfelt
OL,21,Fcondolences.
