OL,3,CWomen have 'traumatic experience' at
OL,4,Cmaternity services, review reveals
OL,6,FFollowing the issues raised in the
OL,7,Freport, Health Secretary Jeremy Miles
OL,8,Fhas escalated Swansea Bay University
OL,9,FHealth Board Maternity and Neonatal
OL,10,FServices to the second highest level
OL,11,Fof intervention.
OL,13,F"I want to offer a full and unreserved
OL,14,Fapology on behalf of the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment to all the women and
OL,16,Ffamilies who have not received the
OL,17,Fservice or care they deserved and
OL,18,Fexpected from Swansea Bay University
OL,19,FHealth Board.
