OL,6,F"The experiences highlighted today;
OL,7,Fthose reflected in the recent Llais
OL,8,Freport and those I heard when I met
OL,9,Ffamilies last month must never happen
OL,10,Fagain."
OL,12,FHe added, "NHS maternity and neonatal
OL,13,Fservices must learn from what has
OL,14,Fhappened in Swansea Bay. Together, we
OL,15,Fmust commit to delivering the best
OL,16,Fpossible experiences and outcomes for
OL,17,Fall women during pregnancy and birth.
